            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Solo SEOs and small teams who want strong briefs plus optimisation.</div>
            <a href="https://frase.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">View pricing →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

