              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best for enterprise content teams</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$170<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Essentials plan</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it delivers</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Cleanest content grader in the category</li>
