            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Operators who already pay for an all-in-one and want on-page bundled.</div>
            <a href="https://www.semrush.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">View pricing →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">07</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Ahrefs</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best backlink-aware on-page</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$129<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
